name: Seven Sisters Necklace with Herkimer Diamond and Pearls

Dakini - are thought to be the enlightened energetic thought-forms of women. Each line in the charm represents the seven warrior goddesses. 

Herkimer Diamonds are another name for double-terminated quartz crystals, which are only found in Herkimer County, New York. It is a very powerful balancer of the body and emotions and often used for relaxation, acceptance of self, clearing of old fears and attunement.

Umbra Sapphire - are thought to promote joy, faith, hope and protection during long journeys. The sapphire stone on this necklace has subtle pink and honey tones.
